OL,3,CWhy hay fever misery last two weeks
OL,4,Clonger than in the 90s
OL,6,FHay fever sufferers now endure
OL,7,Fsymptoms for up to two weeks longer
OL,8,Fthan they did in the 90s, a study has
OL,9,Fclaimed.
OL,11,FClimate change has prolonged the
OL,12,Fpollen season, increasing the amount
OL,13,Fof time people with hay fever are
OL,14,Fexposed to allergens, according to the
OL,15,FLancet Countdown in Europe 2026 report.
OL,17,FHay fever occurs when a person is
OL,18,Fallergic to pollen from trees, grass
OL,19,Fand weeds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
