OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776927916
OL,3,CWhy hay fever misery last two weeks
OL,4,Clonger than in the 90s
OL,6,F"Research and understanding into the
OL,7,Ftiming and length of the different
OL,8,Fpollen seasons is vital to support
OL,9,Fclinicians to ensure treatment and
OL,10,Fmanagement of allergic conditions can
OL,11,Fbe optimised."
OL,13,FA separate allergy strategy,
OL,14,Fspearheaded by charities, patients and
OL,15,Fdoctors, says the UK has some of the
OL,16,Fhighest allergy rates in the world `
OL,17,Fwith 39% of children and 30% of adults
OL,18,Faffected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
