OL,3,CWhy hay fever misery last two weeks
OL,4,Clonger than in the 90s
OL,6,FElsewhere, the report on climate
OL,7,Fchange and health in Europe, which was
OL,8,Fwritten by 65 researchers from 46
OL,9,Facademic and UN institutions, warns of
OL,10,Fheat-related health risks being on the
OL,11,Frise, pointing out that heat health
OL,12,Fwarnings across Europe have increased
OL,13,Fby 318% compared with the 1990s.
OL,15,FHeat health warnings are issued when
OL,16,Fextended periods of hot weather can
OL,17,Fhave an impact on people's health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
