PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776927916
OL,3,CWhy hay fever misery last two weeks
OL,4,Clonger than in the 90s
OL,6,FThe authors point out that nearly all
OL,7,FEuropean regions monitored saw
OL,8,Fincreased numbers of deaths
OL,9,Fattributable to heat during the period
OL,10,Fbetween 2015 and 2024 compared with
OL,11,F1991 to 2000.
OL,13,FIn 2024 alone, they estimated there
OL,14,Fwere about 62,000 deaths in Europe
OL,15,Fattributed to heat.
OL,17,FThe report also highlights that
OL,18,Fclimate change is leading to more
OL,19,Fmosquito-borne viruses being found in
OL,20,FEurope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
